{"tid":891173,"cid":23,"subCid":0,"title":"凱撒你唔好再老屈呀叔我！","createTime":"2018-11-06T01:24:29.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-06T08:47:07.000Z","uid":11779,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"330ce0d57e40556af5285f235427328c88ad183a","tid":891173,"uid":11779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T01:24:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QzemqNC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQzemqNC.jpg&h=ec69b78b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我由頭到尾都冇講過自己係凱薩 黃家進，我只係比人屈做果個社運龍友！你估比條假膠話係佢好光彩呀？我先係受害者。<br />\n黃家進就話我盗用佢身份，講真 我不蛇係攝影界個朵點都響過佢啦！駛扮佢？我扮陳綺貞先生.....唔係...我就算扮柒貓都唔扮佢啦！ <br />\n啲相影到咁都扮佢？哈哈！笑撚死人咩！<br />\n<br />\n射兩幅相大家欣賞下！影到咁都扮佢就係倒自己米！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NDXnUJJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNDXnUJJ.png&h=4b3c6ef6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/y54d1oK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fy54d1oK.png&h=f1723ff6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n黃耀華都靚撚過佢呀！"},{"pid":"dac94514d1419ed2c7795fcc443aecd427449672","tid":891173,"uid":131064,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T01:43:38.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">佢套夏日紀事比人笑到甩碌, 點解天琦果PART咁正,但游雞果PART照妖鏡</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"cff28f424ff2401db3c7b811d580c6cd23ef82d3","tid":891173,"uid":44458,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T04:41:21.000Z","msg":"黃家進你含撚啦<br />\n<br />\n黃    家   進"},{"pid":"2563a341b42506f1373babca8a8e014764215f86","tid":891173,"uid":44458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dac94514d1419ed2c7795fcc443aecd427449672","tid":891173,"uid":131064,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-06T01:43:38.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">佢套夏日紀事比人笑到甩碌, 點解天琦果PART咁正,但游雞果PART照妖鏡</span></strong></span>"},"citedBy"